title: #220: Suicided Saturday Swapcast with Jeffery Wilson and Jeffery Daugherty
description:
Thank you for tuning for another episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli. This is an emergency swap cast with the Conspiracy Farm's Jeffery Wilson and the Christian Whistleblower Jeffery Daugherty to discuss the unexpected but totally expected suicide of Jeffery Epstein.
Huge thank you to Ken Calcaterra for producing this and making this episode happening.
